---
description: Longform writing and essay page quality rules
globs:
  - "app/writing/**/*"
  - "components/typography/**/*"
  - "content/writing/**/*"
---

Writing pages are not blog dashboards.

Requirements:
- optimize line length and line height for long reading sessions
- headings should be elegant, not loud
- links should be visible but not gaudy
- pull quotes should feel literary, not promotional
- use calm rhythm between sections
- avoid excessive UI chrome around prose
- avoid stuffing metadata above the fold

Good additions:
- reading progress
- estimated reading time
- section anchors when text is long
- footnotes or sidenotes when useful

Avoid:
- card-heavy composition inside article pages
- excessive separators
- busy sticky sidebars
- animations that compete with reading
